title: The Legendary Hero is an Academy Honors Student
alternative_titles: Legendary Hero is an Academy Honors Student
summary: The Legendary Hero is an Academy Honors Student Manhwa Five heroes stood against Erebos, the primordial evil that brought the world to the brink of destruction. The Warrior, Arron. The Divine Blacksmith, Dweno. The Poet of the Stars, Luna. The Wise King, Lysinas. And lastly, the Hero of the Beginning, Kyle—me. However, when I was reincarnated, I found that we were all praised as great heroes… Everyone, except for me. A hero academy housing the Hero Records, a gift from the heavens that records the achievements of heroes. I’ll enroll there and find out why I was written out of history. “Why don’t you just go ahead and become an honor student?” Legendary Hero is an Academy Honors Student, 전설급 영웅은 아카데미 우등생
